{"tid":1304563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好辜負咗 林鄭（㐂）嘅一番好意","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T22:10:12.000Z","uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b02f9057b1a35ce39c1f7cb029ba5f27ccefcfcb","tid":1304563,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"見到好多post話大家開始攰，訴求散亂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">㐂</span></span></strong> 媽媽 見狀特登開記者會<br />\n提醒大家 + 幫大家keep住團火<br />\n希望巴絲打們唔好放棄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>攰就抖一抖</ins></span>（唔好抖咁太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n以下少少個人睇法：<br />\n見到幾個post都有巴打提到運動進入樽頸位<br />\n我認為係因為大家見到遊行效用不大 最多只係keep如果國際輿論<br />\n所以其實大家要開始諗諗<br />\n<br />\n1_ <code>（求人）相信中共會開恩放過香港，俾真。雙普選香港人 －－－&gt; 咁就要專注國際輿論戰，促請各國施壓</code><br />\n2_<code>（靠自己）唔奢望中共會妥協／佢口講跪低都唔信 －－－&gt; 咁大家就要諗諗有咩新抗爭方法了</code><br />\n3_<br />\n<code>set唔set deadline，set嘅set幾時，睇埋立法會選成點先？</code><br />\n<br />\n開放討論，<span style=\"color: red;\">有錯請指出</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，不割不譴</span></ins></strong></em></span>"},{"pid":"902d50b5cf125d66443f0279eb107495df02c0d0","tid":1304563,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08f9d1bd188230f6f9d1c901eeedf207ef91589c","tid":1304563,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"902d50b5cf125d66443f0279eb107495df02c0d0","tid":1304563,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"960184508dc4d409f2bdfa59d8c771fe9460bd2b","tid":1304563,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f9d1bd188230f6f9d1c901eeedf207ef91589c","tid":1304563,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"902d50b5cf